subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Dale Earnhardt Jr., considered Nascar’s most popular driver, is in the midst of a slump, and Kyle Busch has been alternately dominating and dumbfounding this year.
